<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kelgaysan, kelgaysan Q191 ҲС27 W56 CA3 ҲСХМ155</title>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.C         Em     Am
 Kelgaysan, kelgaysan,
.F                         C  G
 Haybatli kuch-qudrating bilan!
.      C    Em    Am
 Kelgaysan, kelgaysan,
.F           G          C
 Ey Muqaddas Ruh, kelgaysan

[V2]
.Am              Am/G  F
 Mehr- shavqatli Sen Xudo,
.C       (Gsus)  G
 Duoimni eshitgaysan!
.Am           Am/G   F
 Doim boʻlay huzuringda,
.C             (Gsus) G
 tashnaimni qondirgaysan!
.      C    Em    Am
 Kelgaysan, kelgaysan,
.F           G          C
 Ey Muqaddas Ruh, kelgaysan

[V3]
 Arziysan, arziysan
 Xudoning qurbonlik Qoʻzisi
 Arziysan, arziysan
 Shohlarning Shohi arziysan</lyrics>
<author>Iliyas Tursun</author>
<hymn_number>191</hymn_number>
</song>